        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"openai/gpt-oss-120b:free\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"Renewable energy feed-in in Germany is at {{ $('Code in JavaScript').item.json.renewableFeedIn }}% of total grid load. H1 triggered. Wind onshore: {{ $('Code in JavaScript').item.json.windOnshore }} MW, Solar: {{ $('Code in JavaScript').item.json.solar }} MW, Total load: {{ $('Code in JavaScript').item.json.load }} MW. Which DAX companies BASF, ThyssenKrupp, Covestro, HeidelbergMaterials are most at risk of volatility spike in 24 hours? Under 150 words.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}",
